high_descs: Turn back, go to the other room, turn right when you get to the desk.
Take the caculator pieces that are on the table.
Turn to your back, move and then turn left and go to the next room, turn right, move and then left and move until you are near the wall and cross to the left, face the sofa.
Place the caculator pieces, at the front end of the sofa, after the apple.
Turn left, go ahead, then go to your left to where the microwave is, turn left in front of the microwave.
Open the caculator, open the door and take the dominoes.
Close the microwave door, turn left, move towards the sofa and then turn right, move towards the sofa and then turn left.
Place the domino pieces to the right side of where the calculator and sofa are.
anns.task_desc: Take two sets of caculator pieces to the sofa.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the desk.
Pick up the white caculator from the table.
Turn right to exit the room and reach the larger sofa on the left of the room.
Put the caculator on the sofa.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Take out the caculator from the microwave.
Turn around and walk back to the larger sofa.
Put the caculator behind the other caculator on the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Put two caculators on the sofa.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the desk in the bedroom.
Take the calculator from the table.
Turn around and go near the sofa in living room.
Placed the calculator on the corner of the sofa.
Then turn around and go near the microwave.
Take the another calculator from the oven.
Turn around and go near the sofa.
Placed the calculator on the corner of the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Collect the calculator and placed it on the sofa.
